item.title: Javajdk and mopar java help
item.dc:creator: @Zach1188 Zach1188
item.description:
@Zach1188 wrote:

Actually, there is probably two Admin accounts already on your computer. Make sure you have a password on your current user and log off (the password is so it will stop on the Welcome screen). Once on the welcome screen, press ctrl+alt+del+del (must press del twice!). Now login as “Administrator”, and what ever your administrator password is.

Then try it.
